---
---

<section class="relative py-24 bg-white dark:bg-[#02000d] transition-colors duration-700 overflow-hidden" id="lab">
    <div 
        class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-[3px] animate-argb-fluid opacity-100 dark:opacity-90 shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(99,102,241,0.3)]"
        style="
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #6366f1, #06b6d4, #10b981, #d946ef, #6366f1, #06b6d4, #10b981, #d946ef, #6366f1);
            background-size: 200% 100%;
            mask-image: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, black 15%, black 85%, transparent);
            -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, black 15%, black 85%, transparent);
        "
    ></div>
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-indigo-500/5 dark:bg-indigo-600/5 blur-[120px] -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2 pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
        <div class="text-center mb-20">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-6 tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                Tu flujo de trabajo, <span class="bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 to-cyan-400">sin límites</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-[17px] md:text-xl text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 font-medium max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-snug">
                Optimizá tu productividad al máximo. Un solo dispositivo con infinitas configuraciones para abrir apps, ejecutar macros y controlar tu software favorito.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
            <div class="group relative p-8 rounded-3xl bg-gray-50 dark:bg-white/[0.03] border border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10 hover:border-indigo-500/50 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-indigo-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6 text-indigo-500" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-5 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Programación & Productividad</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-4 text-[14px] text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 font-medium">
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-indigo-500 mt-1.5 shrink-0"></div> 
                        <span>Ejecutá scripts o abrí terminales con un toque.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-indigo-500 mt-1.5 shrink-0"></div> 
                        <span>Accedé a rutas complejas y carpetas al instante.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-indigo-500 mt-1.5 shrink-0"></div> 
                        <span>Automatizá tareas repetitivas de código.</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="group relative p-8 rounded-3xl bg-gray-50 dark:bg-white/[0.03] border border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10 hover:border-cyan-500/50 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-cyan-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-500" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 20h9"/><path d="M16.5 3.5a2.121 2.121 0 0 1 3 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-5 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Diseño & Edición</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-4 text-[14px] text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 font-medium">
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-cyan-500 mt-1.5 shrink-0"></div> 
                        <span>Navegá timelines frame a frame con precisión.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-cyan-500 mt-1.5 shrink-0"></div> 
                        <span>Ajustá pinceles y zoom con fluidez.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-cyan-500 mt-1.5 shrink-0"></div> 
                        <span>Macros para herramientas de diseño complejas.</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="group relative p-8 rounded-3xl bg-gray-50 dark:bg-white/[0.03] border border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10 hover:border-fuchsia-500/50 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-fuchsia-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6 text-fuchsia-500" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 18V5l12-2v13"/><circle cx="6" cy="18" r="3"/><circle cx="18" cy="16" r="3"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-5 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Streaming & Audio</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-4 text-[14px] text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 font-medium">
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-fuchsia-500 mt-1.5 shrink-0"></div> 
                        <span>Cambiá escenas de OBS al instante.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-fuchsia-500 mt-1.5 shrink-0"></div> 
                        <span>Mezclá audio de juego y música.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-fuchsia-500 mt-1.5 shrink-0"></div> 
                        <span>Triggers MIDI y automatizaciones DAW.</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="group relative p-8 rounded-3xl bg-gray-50 dark:bg-white/[0.03] border border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10 hover:border-emerald-500/50 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-emerald-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-500" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="6" width="20" height="12" rx="2"/><path d="M6 12h4"/><path d="M8 10v4"/><circle cx="15" cy="10" r="1"/><circle cx="18" cy="12" r="1"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-5 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Gaming & Inmersión</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-4 text-[14px] text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 font-medium">
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 mt-1.5 shrink-0"></div> 
                        <span>Mapeá cualquier comando o acción al instante.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 mt-1.5 shrink-0"></div> 
                        <span>Sentí la respuesta táctica en cada pulsación.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 mt-1.5 shrink-0"></div> 
                        <span>Elevá tu nivel de inmersión y experiencia.</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

        </div>
        <div class="mt-20 text-center">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-4 px-6 py-3 rounded-full bg-indigo-500/10 border border-indigo-500/20 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 text-sm font-bold">
                <span class="flex h-2 w-2 relative">
                    <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-indigo-400 opacity-75"></span>
                    <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-indigo-500"></span>
                </span>
                Totalmente configurable vía QMK / VIA
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    @keyframes argb-fluid {
        0% { background-position: 0% 0%; }
        100% { background-position: -100% 0%; }
    }
    .animate-argb-fluid {
        animation: argb-fluid 20s linear infinite;
    }
    :global(.dark) section {
        background-image: 
            radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.02) 0%, transparent 40%),
            radial-gradient(circle at 80% 80%, rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.02) 0%, transparent 40%);
    }
</style>
